      "text": "Why did TikTok replace the Creator Fund?"
    },
    {
      "id": "t62",
      "tag": "div",
      "text": "The original Creator Fund paid so little — under $0.004 per 1,000 views — that creators widely criticized it. The Creator Rewards Program aims to pay more by rewarding quality content over raw volume."
    },
    {
      "id": "t63",
      "tag": "button",
      "text": "Can I be in both the Creator Fund and Creator Rewards?"
    },
    {
      "id": "t64",
      "tag": "div",
      "text": "The Creator Rewards Program fully replaced the Fund in most markets. Eligible creators are automatically transitioned to the new system."
    },
